  - Legacy (15+ years): Focus on modernization
  - Growth (5-15 years): Focus on scaling
  - Startup (0-5 years): Focus on foundation
- Digital presence scoring:
  - Missing website: +3 points
  - Poor reviews: +2 points
  - Limited social: +2 points
  - Unclaimed listings: +1 point

3. Vertical Market Scoring (src/industry_configs.py)
