- Compliance indicators (0-2)
- Client portfolio size (0-2)

HVAC Services:
- Building type rating (0-3)
- Service area coverage (0-2)
- Equipment age signals (0-2)

4. Smart Analysis Engine (src/smart_lead_analyzer.py)
- Automated business challenge detection:
  - Website performance issues
  - Review management gaps
  - Social media presence
  - Digital marketing maturity
- Score adjustments based on:
  - Market competition level
  - Geographic business density
  - Seasonal demand patterns

The R27 system implements unique vertical-specific scoring algorithms with dynamic weighting based on real-time market conditions and company-specific factors. The core value lies in its ability to identify high-potential leads based on digital presence gaps and industry-specific opportunity signals.

